data.description: **OPEN HOUSE: Saturday March 9th 11:00am-1:00PM** Built in 2022 Townhome in Daybreak.  Designer Accents throughout. Main level has a perfect Open Concept Family Room with Wainscotting Accent Wall, Additional Windows being the End Unit. Open to the Stunning Kitchen complete with Extra Tall Cabinets, Closet Pantry and Access to Garage off Back of Unit.  Tranquil Master Retreat on 2nd level with Vaulted Ceiling,  Attached En Suit Bathroom with Dual Sink Vanity, Step in Glass Shower and Large Walk In Closet. Two Additional 2nd level Bedrooms and Full Bathroom.  2nd Level Laundry in a Bonus.  Access to all that Daybreak has to offer with Multiple Pools, Gym Access, Lake Access and Easy access to Many of the Open Park Spaces inside Daybreak along with many other amenities.   Square footage figures are provided as a courtesy estimate only.  Buyer is advised to obtain an independent measurement.
